  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rhythm-Based Spellcasting</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel like a true Sorcerer as you gain mastery of the 8 elemental notes and memorize over 100 unique spells.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/ad7a6182002c9008f19713b19f28fd0c.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/ad7a6182002c9008f19713b19f28fd0c.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/ad7a6182002c9008f19713b19f28fd0c.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b5877df4d94d6a22222ce1076fd614cd.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b5877df4d94d6a22222ce1076fd614cd.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b5877df4d94d6a22222ce1076fd614cd.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your Deck and prepare for Battle</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock challenging Boss Battles as you progress through the story.  This fast-paced Card-Battling mode builds upon the skills you gain during the story and pushes them to the limit.  Every spell now has a unique ability - summon powerful creatures, deal direct damage, give yourself buffs, or just even fill your opponent's deck with Toxic Shrooms.  The choice is yours when you build a deck of your own.  Still not hard enough?  Show off your skills online against other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/f2e21375e74e5008fdcab392d79214bd.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/f2e21375e74e5008fdcab392d79214bd.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/f2e21375e74e5008fdcab392d79214bd.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b3f381813d13fe30ba04c35495c51f1a.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b3f381813d13fe30ba04c35495c51f1a.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/b3f381813d13fe30ba04c35495c51f1a.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Narrative Driven Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join <strong>Aiden</strong> and his spirit companion <strong>Silven</strong> as they travel the world learning Sorcery on an impossible quest.  Play over 40 story levels as you discover the truth behind Aiden's spellcasting abilities, despite him being mute. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >User Generated Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still looking for an additional challenge? Create, Upload, and Play levels of your own in the fully functional Level Editor.  Or just download and play levels created by other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
