ts/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/40882b10079b09f033d5d3ec5934d123.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >User Generated Content</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Still looking for an additional challenge? Create, Upload, and Play levels of your own in the fully functional Level Editor.  Or just download and play levels created by other players. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.poster.avif?t=1742309373\" width=594 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.webm?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3056350/extras/bc64462426eaec3475175bb04c8da580.mp4?t=1742309373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
